@Node Requirements "What do you need to run the programs"

 Most of the programs that Nicron Productions make just need a basic
 amiga, with the exceptions of KewlChat which needs a Modem and really
 also a HD but everything we write is for everyone to use so all program
 should just run off a basic amiga.

                            @{"Main Menu" link Main}

@EndNode

@Node Intro "Introduction"

@{b} Nicron Productions@{ub} is a fairly new company but we have been set up to keep
the amiga alive, if no-one else will, we will, we plan to still make good 
programs at cheap prices, thats why most things we make are Freeware except
programs where you get lots of options and took us some time to make.
 ATM there is only 3 programs in are collection but soon it will expand so
look out for the Nicron Productions Logo.
 There is a few ways to get Nicron help and support by either of the
following ways :-

    Email : Nicron@Jinxster.Demon.Co.Uk

    Write : C/O Chris Seward
            10 Scafell Close
            Eastham
            Wirral, Merseyside
            L62 9EU
            ENGLAND

    IRC   : #Nicron  -  Look out for ^Chris^ ask him questions

