@Node New!! "NEW products OUT NOW"

 @{b}Number100@{ub} is a great new game just programmed on the 26/8/96
the idea of the game is to guess what number the computer is thinking of,
ok it may sound like a simple game but once your playing it, it can get
quite good. A built in option is it tells you weather the number you
guessed is higher or lower from the number it's thinking. ATM there is a
load hiscore option, but i'm still trying to get the save to work, at the
moment V0.5 has been released and can be obtained from me for a disk and
stamp or just email me and i'll mime it to you.

 @{b}GuessIt@{ub} is a bit like hangman, only you get as many goes as you
like, you can have a one player game against the computer for Ł1 or 50p if
you use email. There are two cheat modes which can be found out from me for
just an email, this game has been released and can be obtained from me for
and email, send a disk with stamp or can be found on the aminet in
games/think.

                            @{"Main Menu" link Main}

@Endnode

